  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The participation in this clinical study will last approximately 21 weeks with a 1 week
      screening period and a 12 weeks treatment duration. If the study doctor finds, that the
      patients disease has significantly improved he/she will enter a treatment free follow-up
      period of 8 weeks. In total the study consists of 5 to 6 clinical visits (V1 - V6) and 1
      telephone follow-up call.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
